# Swift Package Manager build artifacts
.build/
Package.resolved

# Xcode
# NOTE: the .xcodeproj / .xcworkspace bundles ARE part of the deliverable and
# must be committed (project structure + shared schemes). Only user-specific
# state is ignored. Previously these were ignored wholesale, which is why no
# shared scheme was ever checked in and CI could not build the app.
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcodebuild.log

